text = "Stretch: To Fit Smart
Min Size = (3.0, 0.0)
Max Size = (10.0, 4.0)
The sprite will attempt to stretch while
keeping its scale ratio to 1. If that fails 
then To Fit will be applied
Notice that with a min x size of 3 the 
pink sprite is stretched and keeps its
scale ratio to 1. Meanwhile the green 
text gets squashed due to max y size 
being 3."

